Process called "ldl_tree_n" takes tree as Integer returns Integer:
    @Reasoning
    Returns the ring degree associated with this node.
    @End Reasoning
    @Implementation
    Qword load at offset 40.
    @End Implementation
    @Performance_Hints
    O(1).
    @End Performance_Hints
    @Security_Scope
