End Process

Process called "ldl_tree_is_leaf" takes tree as Integer returns Integer:
    @Reasoning
    1 if this is a sampler leaf, 0 otherwise.
    @End Reasoning
    @Implementation
    Qword load at offset 48.
    @End Implementation
    @Performance_Hints
    O(1).
    @End Performance_Hints
    @Security_Scope
