    Leaf-only sigma value.
    @End Reasoning
    @Implementation
    Float64 load at offset 56.
    @End Implementation
    @Performance_Hints
    O(1).
    @End Performance_Hints
    @Security_Scope
    Internal.
    @End Security_Scope
    Return Memory.memory_get_int64(tree, 56)
End Process

Process called "ldl_tree_set_L01" takes tree as Integer, ptr as Integer returns Integer:
    @Reasoning
    Set the L10 pointer at offset 0.
    @End Reasoning
